data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!!  This beautiful home in the heart of North Port is situated on a large corner lot of .31 acres and is ready for your family to love and call home. Walk in through the tiled entry way with double doors that open into a formal living and dining room, or home office.  Primary bedroom includes ensuite with 2 walk in closets and a linen closet.  The kitchen includes newer appliances and is set up for an easy flow.  Look into the family room from the kitchen that includes a breakfast bar and dinette.  Sliding glass doors are in the primary bedroom, formal dining and dinette that open up onto the screened in porch that overlooks a large fenced back yard that includes mature oak trees. Split bedroom floorplan with large rooms allowing everyone to have their own space.  New roof and exterior paint in 2023, New well equipment 2022. Close to shopping, schools and access to major roads. Call today to schedule your private showing.
